f years of President Obamas tenure in office, even -- again, after all, L=
eader McConnell himself said it best when he acknowledged that our countr=
y was better off -- is better off now than we were when President Obama t=
ook office. And a lot of that is because of the economic strategy that Pr=
esident Obama has pursued to grow our economy from the middle out, to be =
