<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Judge G=
arland&#8217;s schedule this week -- can you give us some detail?<o:p></o:p=
></p>
