<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Well, I =
think the Department of Treasure has indicated that that was the case.&nbsp=
; And those of you who follow these reports closely noticed the difference.=
&nbsp; So I&#8217;m not suggesting that somehow that there hasn&#8217;t bee=
n a change
 in policy, but for how that policy will be implemented moving forward I en=
courage you to check with the Treasury Department.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I haven&#8217;t seen the la=
test legislative proposal from Congress as it relates to Saudi Arabia, but =
