 that there has been some talk on Capitol Hill about potentially revising t=
hat legislation, but I don&#8217;t know where that effort stands at this po=
int.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Can you=
 speak to the question of whether that $116 billion is comprehensive, or ar=
