 And that&#8217;s unfortunate.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">The truth is school admin=
istrators across the country are dealing with an actual dilemma that has co=
nsequences for the safety and dignity of every student at their school.&nbs=
