egal interpretations.&nbsp; They need good ideas that have been used
 by school administrators around the country to address this challenge.&nbs=
p; And that&#8217;s exactly what was provided by the Department of Educatio=
n, and they did that in spite of the cynical political gamesmanship of a lo=
t of Republican politicians across the country.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You m=
